videos.description: Tyler Huntley fumbles the ball and is recovered by San Jose State Ethan Aguayo.
videos.headline: Utah QB Huntley has costly fumble

videos.description: San Jose State QB Montel Aaron gets sacked and fumbles the ball leading to several attempts to recover the fumble, ultimately recovered by Utah.
videos.headline: Loss ball fiasco finally recovered by Utah

videos.description: Tyler Huntley's seven-yard touchdown pass to Darren Carrington extends Utah's lead to 16-3.
videos.headline: After kicking three FGs, Utah finally finds the end zone

videos.description: Samson Nacua attempts to switch hands, but fumbles while falling out of bounds.
videos.headline: Utah fumbles in the red zone

videos.description: Julian Blackmon intercepts Sam Allen's pass at San Jose State's 43-yard line.
videos.headline: Utah's defense forces another turnover

videos.description: Boobie Hobbs long 43-yard punt return puts Utah on the San Jose 48-yard line.
videos.headline: Hobbs' big return puts Utah in good field position

videos.description: Zack Moss just crosses the goal line to give Utah a 30-3 lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Moss bulls his way into the end zone for another Utah TD

videos.description: Trevon Bierria intercepts Tyler Huntley's pass and returns it for two yards to Utah's 47-yard line.
videos.headline: San Jose State's defense forces turnover

videos.description: Josh Love finds Bailey Gaither for a 47-yard pass, leading to San Jose's first touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: San Jose takes advantage of Utah's turnover

videos.description: Utah's coach Kyle Whittingham says his team has to regain momentum and play more disciplined in the second half.
videos.headline: Whittingham: Utah wanted to score another TD and it backfired

videos.description: Tyler Huntley connects with Raelon Singleton for the first time tonight for a 13-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Singleton's first catch results in a TD

videos.description: Tyler Huntley finds Darren Carrington II for a 15-yard touchdown as Utah continues to roll over San Jose State.
videos.headline: Carrington II beats defender, scores third TD

videos.description: Caleb Repp knocks the ball loose for a fumble as John Penisini recovers in San Jose State territory.
videos.headline: Utah forces fourth San Jose State turnover

videos.description: Tyler Nevens has the ball ripped away as Utah's Nick Heninger recovers the loose ball.
videos.headline: Utah's defense forces fifth turnover

videos.description: Devonta'e Henry-Cole's 10-yard touchdown extends Utah's lead to 54-16 with less than a minute to play.
videos.headline: Utah's defense leads to another TD
